svg.metadata: Created by FontForge 20161116 at Thu Feb 3 20:56:01 2011 By Jimmy Warting Telegrama is a typeface that created from the original idea for the relashionship between Pixe and Smoo. At the time of 1992 when I designed these, each of Telegrama Raw and Telegrama Render had another name as the differnt font. These fonts were almost completed, but they had been forgotten until I discovered these in 2008. This time, I united these two fonts as a family. I decided to exhibit these with a little fixing and adding some accented characters, etc.
